** Types of Equilibrium Points
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       871b0c0b-95f2-43f3-bbce-10a5ba1edebb
:END:
[[file:equilibrium_points.png]]
*** Stable
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       0442b908-a7b1-4067-954d-0b9da1405de3
:END:
- The *minimum* of the potential energy graph.
*** Unstable
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       5a5a013b-7785-4807-8ca6-66bdc104c914
:END:
- The *maximum* of the potential energy graph.
*** Neutral
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       9700ce04-f331-42e4-8306-9469ba6bf993
:END:
- Neither maximum nor minimum.
